
BUC Customizer
==============

Description
-----------
Handy tool to customize guest session of public computers in the library of
Fermo (Italy). 

BUC Customizer is based on guest-session-prefs-lightdm by Gunnar Hjalmarsson.
Chances are you shouldn't install this software at all unless you exactely
know what you are doing and why this software has been created.

